name: $resourceType
desc: Returns the FHIR type name for this instance

name: $identifier
desc: Returns: Unique code or number identifying the location to its users.

name: $addidentifier
desc: Unique code or number identifying the location to its users.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: Unique code or number identifying the location to its users.

name: $status
desc: Returns: The status property covers the general availability of the resource, not the current value which may be covered by the operationStatus, or by a schedule/slots if they are configured for the location.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The status property covers the general availability of the resource, not the current value which may be covered by the operationStatus, or by a schedule/slots if they are configured for the location.

name: $operationalStatus
desc: Returns: The operational status covers operation values most relevant to beds (but can also apply to rooms/units/chairs/etc. such as an isolation unit/dialysis chair). This typically covers concepts such as contamination, housekeeping, and other activities like maintenance.

pvardefs.name: pValue

name: $::name
desc: Returns: Name of the location as used by humans. Does not need to be unique.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Name of the location as used by humans. Does not need to be unique.

name: $alias
desc: Returns: A list of alternate names that the location is known as, or was known as, in the past.

name: $addalias
desc: A list of alternate names that the location is known as, or was known as, in the past.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A list of alternate names that the location is known as, or was known as, in the past.

name: $description
desc: Returns: Description of the Location, which helps in finding or referencing the place.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Description of the Location, which helps in finding or referencing the place.

name: $mode
desc: Returns: Indicates whether a resource instance represents a specific location or a class of locations.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Indicates whether a resource instance represents a specific location or a class of locations.

name: $::type
desc: Returns: Indicates the type of function performed at the location.

name: $addtype
desc: Indicates the type of function performed at the location.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: Indicates the type of function performed at the location.

name: $telecom
desc: Returns: The contact details of communication devices available at the location. This can include phone numbers, fax numbers, mobile numbers, email addresses and web sites.

name: $addtelecom
desc: The contact details of communication devices available at the location. This can include phone numbers, fax numbers, mobile numbers, email addresses and web sites.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: The contact details of communication devices available at the location. This can include phone numbers, fax numbers, mobile numbers, email addresses and web sites.

name: $address
desc: Returns: Physical location.

name: $physicalType
desc: Returns: Physical form of the location, e.g. building, room, vehicle, road.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Physical form of the location, e.g. building, room, vehicle, road.

name: $position
desc: Returns: The absolute geographic location of the Location, expressed using the WGS84 datum (This is the same co-ordinate system used in KML).

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The absolute geographic location of the Location, expressed using the WGS84 datum (This is the same co-ordinate system used in KML).

name: $managingOrganization
desc: Returns: The organization responsible for the provisioning and upkeep of the location.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The organization responsible for the provisioning and upkeep of the location.

name: $partOf
desc: Returns: Another Location of which this Location is physically a part of.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Another Location of which this Location is physically a part of.

name: $hoursOfOperation
desc: Returns: What days/times during a week is this location usually open.

name: $addhoursOfOperation
desc: What days/times during a week is this location usually open.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: What days/times during a week is this location usually open.

name: $availabilityExceptions
desc: Returns: A description of when the locations opening ours are different to normal, e.g. public holiday availability. Succinctly describing all possible exceptions to normal site availability as detailed in the opening hours Times.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A description of when the locations opening ours are different to normal, e.g. public holiday availability. Succinctly describing all possible exceptions to normal site availability as detailed in the opening hours Times.
